title: DDFP 505: Week 10 Red Challenge Flag picks & Picking a Franchise QB
itunes:title: DDFP 505: Week 10 Red Challenge Flag picks & Picking a Franchise QB
description:
Shek is joined by Matt "Money" Smith, Matt Harmon and Handsome Hank as they give Shek some fantasy football advice and discuss which QB they would want for the next 18 months. Then, the fellas read some new "Dad Jokes" and hear some of EmmaVP's new scrumptious Week 10 game previews as they transform Studio 66 into Japanese restaurant, "Sushi Shek's" for Red Challenge Flag picks.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
